data.description: Incredible opportunity! 6 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 2 half baths, approx 5000sf home with a walk-out basement and in-law suite. Located on 1.18 acres, in the Ravine Ridge community, in the Westerville SD, at the end of a cul-de-sac with a wooded, private lot w/2 Ravines meeting in the back. Lots of windows to show off the views, vaulted great room w/plank ceiling, double tray ceilings, molding and wainscoting, hardwood floors, granite counters and custom built, solid wood cabinets.This was the community builder's personal home which has all of the upgrades you'd want, however it does need some work. Professional photos coming soon.
